dct_description_sm: Relief shown by contours and spot heights. Series in 4 sheets numbered 1 to 4. Coverage is of Belgium and northern France. Includes index to adjoining sheets. Originally issued folded to 18 x 11 cm. Historic Maps set is incomplete.
dct_creator_sm: Great Britain. War Office. General Staff. Geographical Section
dct_publisher_sm: [London] : War Office, Geographical Section, General Staff, 1915.
